# Outside Inn — Internal Strategy Doc
**Last updated: February 6, 2026**
**Audience: EIW + AI planning sessions**

---

## What This Is

Outside Inn is a 24/7 LoFi fantasy radio station. Original music plays over a looping pixel art animation of Holdt — a steampunk Holden Caulfield — writing at a desk inside a stone inn. The tagline is "Step inn anytime and stay."

The station runs on rails. No interruptions, no talking head, no schedule. Someone leaves it on for a 6-hour work session, comes back tomorrow, does it again. Reliability is the product.

E.I. Werner is a completely separate channel — gaming, writing, personal content. The brands share a world and an audience pipeline, but never the same stream.

